INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Fire and Water Stickman', 502, 'Are you ready for the adventure of Fire and Water? In this journey, you need to help them. The stick figures must be quick and reach the portal as fast as possible. You need to be fast to survive in the block world. The block world is full of dangers. This is just the beginning of the adventure, but reach the portal and start the journey. Watch out for spikes and spinning wheels; they are everywhere. Find the keys in the houses and collect them. Without keys, the portal wont open.', 'Move to WASD Arrow Keys Double Jump available Mobile Touch Control', 'English'),
('Gun Shooting Range', 503, 'In this game, you are a rookie sniper at the beginning, take your rifle, pass all the missions,and grow into a professional sniper! Remember, shoot every bullet calmly, be accurate and fatal,and use the least bullets to do the biggest damage.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('DIY Slime Simulator ASMR', 504, 'DIY Slime Simulator ASMR is a simulation game. This game includes a variety of ways to play with Slime. Not only can you pinch it and squeeze it, you can also make unique slime. Add slime to the bowl, add dye, add some decorations, and mix them well. When you pinch the slime, we also accompany it with decompression sound effects. You can create all kinds of slimes and collect them. Become the king of slime collection.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Noob vs Obby Two Player', 505, 'Are you ready for the eternal battle between Noob and Obby? Weapons are drawn, and the war has begun. Choose your side in this war and start fighting with your friend. Whether you choose to be an Obby or a Noob, aim to win the war. You must battle against your friend. Use bombs, guns, and stones to defeat and kill your enemy. To win, eliminate your opponent and emerge victorious.', 'Player 1 can move with the WASD keys You can shoot with the S key Player 2 can move with the Arrow Keys keys You can shoot with the Down Arrow key Mobile play is available', 'English'),
('Animal: Find The Differences', 506, 'Animal: Find the Difference is a fun and engaging puzzle game where players test their observation skills by spotting differences between pairs of animal-themed images. Each level presents two seemingly identical pictures with subtle variations, challenging players to identify and tap on the differences before time runs out. Perfect for all ages, this game combines entertainment with cognitive exercise, making it a delightful and educational experience.', 'Use your mouse or touchpad to click on the differences between the two images Simply move the cursor over the area you think is different and click to highlight the discrepancy', 'English'),
('Animal Preserver', 507, 'Use your brain to rescue the Animals from the deadly Bees. Deadly Bees are waiting to attack the Animals, you have to use your brain and draw safety zones for those needy Animals. Be careful! While drawing the lines as the wrong zone means the game will be over, use low lines to collect 3 stars. Features of this game: Features of this game: High Quality graphics will leave only positive feedback Game size is minimal (but not compromised the graphics) and it is good for your device health Super simple controls make it easy to start playing Interesting quests will not let you get bored while playing the game.', 'How to play Android Use On-Screen Tap amp Draw PC Use Mouse Left Click amp Hold to draw', 'English'),
('Blocks Vs Pirates', 508, 'Blocks Vs Pirates is an exciting sports game to play for all ages. Dive into this technical game that tests your aiming ability to make a goal. The challenge is simple yet thrilling: how long can you stay in the game? Your endurance is determined by how well you can aim. Calculate the right angle and degree of force and launch the Ninja through into the basket! In Blocks Vs Pirates, you need to master the art of precision. Each level presents new obstacles and challenges, ensuring that the game remains engaging and stimulating.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Speedy vs Steady', 509, 'Speedy vs Steady A Race of Rabbit and Tortoise! In this classic Snakes &amp;amp; Ladders game, youll choose to play as the speedy Rabbit or the steady Tortoise. The Rabbit and the Tortoise move either manually or automated way while dice outcomes are really random. Will you rely on pure speed or calculated moves to reach the finish line first.', 'Roll dice and move ahead', 'English'),
('Nano Ninjas', 510, 'Welcome to Nano Ninjas running Game! Run and dodge obstacles and collect coins! Collect coins to unlock new characters and start a new adventure. Enjoy! Website developer &lt;a href=''https://www.vodogame.com/''&gt;https://www.vodogame.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Left and right arrows to move Down arrow to slide Up arrow to shoot Space button to jump', 'English'),
('Magic Finger Puzzle 3d', 511, 'Magic Finger Puzzle 3D is an interesting casual puzzle online game. You have an amazing pair of hands that can fire the laser. It can help you smash the cages that are holding you. It can also launch boxes onto barricades so that you can escape from the cage without stepping on spikes and dying. But dont worry, you need to use your ingenuity to make good use of those amazing hands. All difficulties will be solved. Join the game if you want to try a journey full of adventure.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('holey battle royale', 512, 'Holey battle royale game where you consume various items and opponents with smaller holes. You will grow bigger as you swallow! The map will continuously shrink, forcing players into a narrower environment until there is only one person left standing. Consume, grow, and become the last hole standing in the arena!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Panda The Cake Maker', 513, 'Make delicious Cakes with the Panda Chef, take order and do successful delivery. Panda chef and his assistant own a Cake shop. They are working very hard to keep their Cake quality better, and they want to satisfy their customers at any cost. Now the player has to help the Panda chef to make ordered cakes as the customer needs. Be careful! While making the cakes, as customers will be dissatisfied if any wrong ingredients are added in their cakes, the game will be over. So make cakes delicious and beautiful and help Panda to make more coins. Features of this game: High Quality graphics Game size is minimal Super simple controls.', 'How to play Android Use On-Screen touch buttons to control the player PC Mouse Left Click to drag and drop', 'English'),
('Space Patrol', 514, 'Patrol the space and Kill the Alien Spiders, Collect crystals to reach the next destination. Explore the space world and mysterious Alien spiders execute it and more exciting challenges waiting for the player. Be Careful! While exploring the space world as Alien Spider is very dangerous and deadly traps can harm the player and game will be over. If you like genres such as adventure, action, rpg, platform, quests or just want to have a good time then this game is for you. Features of this game: High Quality graphics Game size is minimal Super simple controls Interesting quests.', 'How to play Android Use On-Screen touch buttons to control the player PC Move Left - Press ldquo A rdquo Move Right - Press ldquo D rdquo Jump - Press ldquo W rdquo Jet-Pack - Press ldquo J rdquo Shoe-Jet - Press ldquo K rdquo Fire - Press l', 'English'),
('Merge Crypto   2048 Puzzle', 515, 'Welcome to the joyful world of Merge Crypto. This game is an interesting and classic casual game where you can relax and kill time at any moment. The rules of Merge Crypto are extremely simple and easy to grasp. You just need to continuously combine balls of the same cryptocurrency until you reach the final goal of creating a Bitcoin Ball, which gives an increased score booster. Moreover, its a great way to train your brain and fingers, and its entertainment for all ages.', 'Swipe to aim at the ball of the same currency Release your finger to throw it Two balls merge into one larger one upon impact Dont let the balls accumulate beyond the warning line', 'English'),
('Snake Cube', 516, 'Snake Cube is a game in which you need to control a snake and collect cubes that move along different trajectories, also avoiding obstacles and collisions.', 'Use the arrow keys to move A to increase the speed S to decrease For mobile use the in-game buttons', 'English'),
('Animals Pare', 517, 'Exciting 60 levels and cute animals are waiting for you, each of which needs to find a pair! This game will help the development of memory and will delight with pleasant graphics. The further the levels go, the more complex the mechanics are waiting for you!', 'Mouse click or tap tChoose a level and try to find a pair among the suggested cards as soon as possible By clicking on the card it turns over the reverse side and you need to remember where which card is located The further the levels go the more comp', 'English'),
('Letterland Lollipops', 518, 'Welcome to Letterland Lollipops! In this fun game, youll learn to identify both lowercase and uppercase letters from A to Z. Match the yummy lollipops with the same letter to score points and unlock new levels. Get ready for a sweet and educational adventure!', 'Click and hold then move to go to appropriate letter lollipop', 'English'),
('Makeover Spa Dress Up', 519, 'Makeover Spa Dress Up is a simulation game. Lucy is going on a very important date, and shes getting ready to dress up. First help her do a complete facial SPA, light up the charming aromatherapy, carefully clean her face, and help her have flawless skin. Then it&amp;rsquo;s time to do her hair. She wants to have the most fashionable hairstyle. Can you help her do the lost fashionable hairstyle? Then its time to put on makeup and dress up. Help her put on lipstick, eye shadow, eyeliner, and blush, so that she can maximize her charm. Finally, wear clothes made by top designers. Today&amp;rsquo;s outfit is complete! Lucy is leaving for a date!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Worm Colors', 520, 'Swipe your finger left and right to guide your worm through the colorful shapes. Try to pass only on the same color as your worm and do not touch other shapes with different color than the worm. Explore tons of amazing and challenging levels and try to complete them all. Enjoy!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Crushy Birds', 521, 'ChatGPT Crushy Birds is an engaging and fast-paced browser game where players must eliminate birds by clicking on them as they fly across the screen. The game features colorful, cartoonish graphics that appeal to players of all ages. Each successful click scores points, with the game increasing in difficulty as more birds appear and fly faster. Strategic clicks and sharp reflexes are essential to achieve high scores in this addictive and fun-filled challenge.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
