('Infinity Cubes 2048', 655, 'Infinity Cubes 2048 with funny physics. Merge identical cubes and enjoy their funny physics. Get the biggest cube! Have a good game!', 'Controls on mobile phone Moving the area with the cube Touch the screen and move your finger along the horizon Drop the cube down Release your finger from the screen Mouse control Moving the area with the cube Hold down the Right mouse button and', 'English'),
