('Cannons Blast 3D', 672, 'Cannons Blast 3D plays like another tower defense puzzle game. With a heavy machine gun and a cannon, you need to eliminate all incoming enemy units before they get close to your castle. Your weapon has limited ammo and reloading speed. It is necessary to make a choice of fire coverage. When you earn enough gems, you can buy the other 2 weapons and upgrade your current ones. It is time to test your shooting skills!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Peanut Butter Jelly Sandwich', 673, 'Peanut Butter Jelly Sandwich is an exquisite Cooking Game. In this game, you will learn to make delicious Sandwiches. We have provided you with recipes for Peanut Butter Jelly Sandwich and Chicken Sandwich. You can choose anyone and start your production. You dont need to have superb cooking skills, you just need to follow the tips and operate step by step to make delicious food. This game also has bright colors and a realistic ainting style, which will definitely make you fall in love with making delicious food.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pixel Racer', 674, 'Get in a nostalgic journey with Pixel Racer, a thrilling 2D pixel art racing game where you take control of a vibrant red car, weaving through a bustling highway filled with unpredictable traffic. Your objective is simple yet challenging: dodge all the other vehicles and slippery oil spills that come your way. Precision and quick reflexes are your best allies as you strive to survive for as long as possible. The longer you last, the higher your score climbs. Relive the golden age of arcade gaming with Pixel Racer and see how long you can keep your car on the road!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Offroad Truck Animal Transporter', 675, 'Experience the thrill of offroad trucking in Offroad Truck Animal Transporter. Navigate through a realistic forest environment, transporting various farm animals to their destinations. With 10 challenging levels, youll drive through rugged terrain, face unpredictable weather, and tackle obstacles. Each level tests your driving skills and precision. Can you master the art of farm animal transport and complete all levels? Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesonline.com/''&gt;https://www.crazygamesonline.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Drive your truck using wasd change camera C click on the screen and can look around', 'English'),
('House of Mystery', 676, 'After entering one of the rooms you have to find all the hidden objects. The names of the items you need to find will appear on the left side. You need to concentrate well and find all the objects in the room. You have to watch the time, because if it runs out it will be game over. Try to get the maximum points and three stars in every room.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('DoctorDot Connect Mania', 677, 'Match the colors and dont meet any object of different color anywhere. Tap top open the gate between two blue circles and make the pink circles meet the last circle which is pink too. Enjoy!', 'Let the same color objects match Tap to open the path between blue circles', 'English'),
('Block Team Deathmatch', 678, 'Block Team Deathmatch is a first-person shooting simulation game. All models are made of pixel blocks including scenes, characters, and weapons. We have 4v4 Team Mode, Individual Mode, and Sniper Mode for you to select. If I were you, I would play the Team Mode first for better equipment, then challenge the other 2 modes when the rank levels up. If you never played any shooting games, I recommend you buy an auto-rifle to fight at any distance. Keep calm and shoot first!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Solitaire Crime Stories', 679, 'Solitaire Crime Stories is an exciting new Solitaire game which will carry you away into a world of fascinating criminal investigations, colorful characters and stunning locations. Test your skills by completing interesting levels and unraveling the mysteries of the town of Springdale! Springdale is a small American town that lives in peace and quiet... but that&amp;rsquo;s only at first glance. Everyone hides secrets here, secrets that could tear this carefree town apart. Mysterious murders and dark family secrets are only some of the riddles for our young journalist heroine Lana Whitt to unravel.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Blocky Challenges', 680, 'A friend is one who will not leave in trouble, will always tell the truth and will not ask too much. If you have it, then you are very lucky, because there are never many friends. Our hero in the game Blocky Challenges also has friends and they will come to his aid if you call them. The red block with funny eyes sets off on a journey full of all sorts of obstacles. Block did not at all think that he had no opportunity to jump over even the smallest bump, not exactly a high obstacle. But the hero will succeed. Because as soon as you click and the required number of blocks will be formed under it, which will raise it to the required height.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ropeway Master', 681, 'Ropeway Master is a new challenging puzzle game. You should utilize the rope to free everyone,control the rope, overcome the obstacles, and complete the demanding and unique puzzle game. The game is not difficult! Drag the rope to make a safe path, control the rope, and rescue veryone.Dont forget to avoid the obstacles along the way. If you play Rope Puzzle, make sure you do nothing. You will play for hours and linger.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
