('World of Alice   Star Sequence', 716, 'World of Alice - Star Sequence World of Alice - Star Sequence is an educational game developed for children where they will learn numbers and numerical sequences through star constellations in a fun way from their cell phone, tablet or computer. Excellent educational resource. In World of Alice, learning is fun.', 'Click on the next number to complete the numerical sequence', 'English'),
('Baby Games For Preschool Kids', 717, 'Baby Games For Preschool Kids is a very cute educational game at yiv.com. This baby games:2+ kids, and toddlers, has 3 parts for you to experience. They are Happy Island, Forest Adventure, and Cheerful Games. There are 3 mini-games in each of these 3 sections. These mini-games are good for you to exercise your ability to distinguish between size, color, shape, and animal species. If you are looking for a game that combines fun and entertainment, this game is definitely the best choice. Have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Adam vs Sacha', 718, 'While Adam and Sacha were best friends, they got into a fight and as a result, they tried to destroy each other. To do this, they collected weapons falling from the air on three different maps and shot each other.', 'W A D for Sacha movement Arrow keys for Adam movement Mobile touch screen button', 'English'),
('Wobble Robber Man', 719, 'Wobble Man is a casual game where your objective is to help a suit-clad man navigate upstairs without being detected. To achieve this, you must carefully observe your surroundings and utilize various tools you gather to unlock doors or rearrange furniture. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.kizi10.org/''&gt;https://www.kizi10.org/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Baby Panda Forest Recipes', 720, 'Baby Panda Forest Recipes is a very cute cooking game. there are three fun parts in this game. You can choose to make delicious rice balls with the bunny. You can also choose to make novelty coconut jelly with the little monkey. You can also choose to make groundnut cake with the little mole. The game has smooth HD animations. There are also bright colors. You just need to follow the tips to make the food. Enjoy.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
