('Kiki World', 726, 'Decorate and Makeover your home sweet home with Kiki World: Kawaii Doll Decor! Introducing Kiki World: Kawaii Doll Decor, a home decor game designed exclusively for your aesthetic interior design passions. Dive into the world of decor, where clicking, dragging, and dropping chic furniture transforms empty spaces into captivating living areas. Your dream home is here. Take away the trash, throw away old and dirty things! Lets have a home makeover with Kiki World: Kawaii Doll Decor!', 'Perfect for those who love to fantasize about room transformations and have a keen eye for home aesthetics Start designing your ideal living space now and bring your decor dreams to life with Kiki World Kawaii Doll Decor', 'English'),
('Code Runner: Binary Confusion', 727, 'A fast-paced binary runner where logic and reflexes collide. Match the rule, dodge the wrong digit &amp;mdash; survive the code! .A psychological runner puzzle where every second counts and one rule could change everything.', '1 Swipe left right or use arrow keys to switch lanes 2 Watch the active rule top of screen 3 Follow the rule carefully mdash each mistake costs a life', 'English'),
