('Can You Catch', 736, 'Do you trust your reflexes? lets try it. In this simple game, you need to quickly collect the gold coins falling from above. Be careful, if you cannot collect them, you will lose. Try to score the most.', 'It is played with the a and d keys or the right and left arrow keys on the keyboard', 'English'),
('Word Puzzle Travel', 737, 'Word Puzzle Travel offers an exciting journey through language and exploration. In this captivating game, players embark on a virtual voyage filled with word puzzles inspired by destinations around the globe. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.bestcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.bestcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt; From famous landmarks to cultural icons, each level presents unique challenges that test players vocabulary and problem-solving skills.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
