('Openworld Racing', 740, 'Openworld Racing is a simple and fun 3D driving game where you can explore a large open world at your own pace. Drive through streets, enjoy smooth handling, and switch between three different cars. &amp;bull; Open World Exploration &amp;ndash; Drive anywhere with no limits. &amp;bull; Day &amp;amp; Night Cycle &amp;ndash; Experience changing lighting as time passes. &amp;bull; Mobile &amp;amp; PC Controls &amp;ndash; Easy-to-use touch icons on mobile, WASD controls on PC (more controls shown in-game). &amp;bull; Switch Cars Anytime &amp;ndash; Try out all 3 cars and feel the difference. &amp;bull; Camera Modes &amp;ndash; Change perspective for the best driving view. Whether you want to drift, cruise, or just explore&amp;mdash;Openworld Racing is all about fun and freedom.', 'Mobile Tap arrow icons to move brake icon to stop headlight icon to toggle front lights and camera icon to change perspective PC Use WASD to drive More controls are shown in the top-left corner of the game', 'English'),
('Scooter Touchgrind Tricks 3D', 741, 'Scooter Touchgrind Tricks 3D is a fun driving game where you control a scooter through exciting levels full of obstacles. Your goal is simple&amp;mdash;reach the finish line without crashing! Along the way, you&amp;rsquo;ll need to dodge obstacles and keep your balance as the tracks get harder. You can collect coins to unlock cooler scooters and try out different styles. With smooth controls and tons of levels to beat, this game keeps you coming back for more. Whether youre into racing or just love doing tricks, its all about skill, speed, and having fun on two wheels.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
