('Obby vs Bacon Rainbow Parkour', 753, 'Are you ready to dive into a life full of obstacle courses with Obby and Bacon? You must complete the courses. Be careful, enemies are everywhere. Sometimes the courses can be very difficult. Watch out for spikes and falling balls from the sky. You and your friend need to reach the flag at the finish line together. If both friends reach the flag, you earn the right to move to the next level. Collect all the coins on the course with your friend. Gather all the coins and reach the flag.', 'The Yellow player moves using the WASD keys The Grey player moves using the arrow keys Collect all the coins Mobile gameplay mobile touch control is available', 'English'),
('Baby Panda Dream Job', 754, 'Baby Panda Dream Job is a very interactive and educational game. If you want to have fun while learning about the various professions, then this is the game for you. In this game, you can experience three jobs, bakery clerk, courier, and construction worker. You will learn how to choose the bread that customers like, how to build a complete house out of bricks, and how to send a delivery from the delivery station to the customer. This game has very fine interactive features to keep you engaged. It also has a thoughtful voice feature.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Beat the Boss', 755, 'Few of us are delighted with our bosses, as a rule, they are not very fond of them, even if they are quite loyal to their subordinates. This is ungrateful human nature. But the boss in our game Beat the Boss is really insufferable. He humiliates his subordinates, burdens them with backbreaking work, and then punishes for failure to comply. Everyone hates him and wants nothing more, nothing less - a cruel death. However, no one wants to go to jail, so they can only kill the hated boss in their own image. Especially for harsh situations, our game was invented, where you can pour out your anger on the virtual boss.', 'Use mouse or touch on the screen', 'English'),
('Football King', 756, 'Football King offers a highly engaging gameplay experience where players can select their character and customize their teams flag, adding a personal touch to the competition. You can tackle the game solo in an exhilarating single-player tournament mode, where you&amp;rsquo;ll challenge sophisticated AI teams that adapt to your gameplay style. Website dev &lt;a href=''https://unblocked-games.s3.amazonaws.com/index.html''&gt;https://unblocked-games.s3.amazonaws.com/index.html&lt;/a&gt;', 'Arrow keys to move space to shoot B for power shot', 'English'),
('Princess Beauty Dress Up Girl', 757, 'Princess Beauty Dress-Up Girl is a super sophisticated makeup and dress-up game. Two lovely princesses have become gray after a day of fun. But they need to go to the photo studio to have their pictures taken. As their royal stylist. Use your fashion talents and help them to freshen up. First, choose a princess and then help her start her transformation. You need to clean her face first and then help her apply a hydrating mask. The princess has some heavy dark circles under her eyes, so dont forget to take care of her eyes. Eyebrows can show a persons temperament, so remember to trim the princesss eyebrows.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Stickman Team Return', 758, 'Its team time now! Cartoon character The game of Team Detroit is fun to watch. A gang of robbers is threatening the city of Detroit, but three little stick figures will come together to stop them. Take pleasure in killing off enemy stickmen while using any of the three playable characters. Because of their unique abilities and weaponry, each playable character is tailor-made for their specific role.', 'Controls Player 1 WASD move Spacebar Shoot E Special Player 2 Keyboard arrows J Shoot K Special C Change character', 'English'),
('World of Alice   Numbers Shapes', 759, 'World of Alice - Numbers Shapes World of Alice - Numbers Shapes is an educational game developed for children where they will learn the shapes of numbers in a fun way using their cell phone, tablet or computer. Excellent educational resource. In World of Alice, learning is fun.', 'Drag the corresponding number to the shape', 'English'),
('Wobble Rope 3D', 760, 'We have a passion for casual and hyper-casual games, so we decided to try out a new one featuring a wobbly man attempting to climb down a mountain using a rope. The wobbly man wobbles around, jumping from the mountain, which makes the game far more interesting, addictive, and competitive.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Park Inc', 761, 'Park Inc is an engaging mobile game where players embark on a thrilling parking adventure. The objective? Unlock cars trapped in tight parking spots by strategically dragging vehicles to freedom. With each level presenting increasingly challenging puzzles, players must showcase their spatial awareness and problem-solving skills to succeed. Whether youre a casual gamer or a seasoned parking pro, Park Inc offers hours of addictive fun for all skill levels. Website Developer', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
