('Dogland', 764, 'Improve yourself by touching the food bowl in a world full of dogs.You can get yourself some new bones from the land of the dogs. Or you can get magic pickaxes from the wise old purple wizard dog.', 'Click on the screen to earn money Click on buttons and travel to get upgrades Click on it to get the improvements', 'English'),
