('Ludo Maximus', 777, 'Roll the dice, strategize your moves, and experience the timeless joy of Ludo! Play offline, enjoy smart AI opponents. Ludo is the ultimate mobile rendition of the classic board game. Download now for endless fun and become the Ludo Master! #Ludo #BoardGameFun Key Features: Classic Gameplay Complete with Smart AI components Family-Friendly Endless Fun', 'Click Dice on your turn and play simple Ludo this time too Reset at home screen if you want to enter your own names for players', 'English'),
('Watermelon Merge 5', 778, 'Watermelon Merge is a charming and enjoyable puzzle adventure where players combine identical fruits to grow them into larger ones, ultimately forming a complete watermelon. Featuring both classic gameplay and innovative modes, it offers something for everyone. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesx.com/''&gt;https://www.crazygamesx.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Mech Monster Arena', 779, 'Mech Monster Arena is a robot-fighting turn-based strategy game. Differently in this fighting game, you dont need to learn how to operate the robot and release each skill. You only need to learn the basic skill counter rules and select the skills flexibly. By earning EXPs and coins from battles in Mech Battle, you can fight with AI opponents and develop your robot. When you have some sources to upgrade your robot in the Mech Warehouse, you can challenge other players in the Arena. Have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Real Pool 3D', 780, 'Real Pool 3D offers an immersive gaming experience with its diverse range of levels. Whether youre a novice or a seasoned player, theres a challenge suited for you. Dive into various skill levels, from easy to expert, and test your cue skills in different environments. With each level presenting unique obstacles and layouts, youll constantly find yourself engaged and striving for mastery. Get ready to sink those shots and conquer the pool table! Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.playbestgames.online/''&gt;https://www.playbestgames.online/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
