('Draw To Win Stars', 789, 'Draw To Win Stars is a unique game where you use your drawing skills to connect and guide a plant to collect all the stars in each level. With creative and strategic drawing, you navigate through obstacles and puzzles, aiming to gather every star along the way. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.playbestgames.io/''&gt;https://www.playbestgames.io/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Drawer And Race', 790, 'In Drawer And Race, participants compete to accurately depict a given word or phrase through quick drawings. Its a fast-paced game where players race against the clock to convey their chosen word, often employing simple and intuitive sketches. The emphasis is on speed and clarity, challenging players to think on their feet and express ideas concisely. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.game-plays.com/''&gt;https://www.game-plays.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cave Worker Steve', 791, 'Steve, who works in the cave to protect and develop his village, collects money by breaking the blocks in the cave. By saving this money, he can increase his pickaxe to stone, iron, gold, diamond and emerald levels. He can cast a spell on his pickaxe from the enchantment table and turn his pickaxe into its most powerful state.', 'Click on the screen to earn money Use the signs to go to the village or the enchanted table Click on it if you can afford to buy something', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
