('Watermelon Merge 4', 797, 'Watermelon Merge 4is a delightful and engaging puzzle experience where players merge matching fruits to cultivate larger ones, culminating in the creation of a complete watermelon. Offering both classic gameplay and innovative modes, it caters to diverse preferences. Whether you prefer traditional challenges or crave fresh twists, theres an option for you. Website Developer &lt;a href=''https://www.kizi10.org/''&gt;https://www.kizi10.org/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Extreme Car Driving Parking', 798, 'In this Extreme Car Driving simulator game 2024, you will enjoy driving and parking levels. You may have played many real car parking games but this parking simulator 2024 is different from all those car driving games as you have to obey all traffic rules to park your modern car in the parking zone. Get these free 3D car games to enjoy every level of ultimate car driving &amp;amp; parking games.', 'Keyboard Arrow Controls', 'English'),
('Obby Minecraft Ultimate', 799, 'Obby Parkour Ultimate 3D is a fun skill-based game. Enjoy 35 distinct levels with diverse mechanics and a very challenging parkour jumping gaming experience. Make your way to the finish with your favorite Obby and Mine characters by jumping platforms, avoiding spikes, and completing all levels to unlock new characters.', 'Desktop Controls Mouse to move camera WASD to move Spacebar Jump Mobile Controls Use the game buttons to move jump', 'English'),
('Racer Car', 800, 'In the game Racer Car, players are invited to an exhilarating adventure that tests their speed, reflexes, and concentration. While navigating a car on the highway, the goal is to travel as far as possible without colliding with other vehicles. This game challenges players skills in speed, reaction time, and maintaining focus. Every passing second increases the players score, encouraging them to play for longer durations to achieve higher scores. Racer Car offers simple controls, stunning graphics, and addictive gameplay that captivates players and keeps them glued to the screen. Test your skills to become the king of the highway and', 'Press the A key to move the car to the left Press the D key to move the car to the right On mobile devices players can simply swipe their finger left or right on the screen to move the car accordingly', 'English'),
('Nuts And Bolts Sort', 801, 'Nuts And Bolts Sort - Puzzle Game Introduction Looking for a game that is both challenging and relaxing? Look no further than Nuts And Bolts Sort - the ultimate brain training challenge that doubles as a stress-relieving escape.', 'How to play the nut bolt game Imagine a pile of nuts of different colors scattered all over the place Your task as a nut sort master is to sort them out by color onto corresponding bolt Sounds simple right Think again The nuts and bolts game presen', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
